<text id="02-output-contract" title="Puppeteer Launch &amp; Navigation Setup Output Contract" version="2.0.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema for the config artefact this methodology produces. Validator enforces required keys + per-field constraints + forbidden patterns.</summary>

  <section title="Schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/puppeteer-launch-setup.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": [
    "env",
    "sandbox_flags_set",
    "chromium_pinned",
    "cache_dir_set",
    "close_in_finally",
    "default_wait_until"
  ],
  "properties": {
    "env": {
      "enum": [
        "local",
        "docker",
        "ci",
        "serverless"
      ]
    },
    "sandbox_flags_set": {
      "type": "boolean"
    },
    "chromium_pinned": {
      "type": "boolean",
      "const": true
    },
    "cache_dir_set": {
      "type": "boolean"
    },
    "close_in_finally": {
      "type": "boolean",
      "const": true
    },
    "default_wait_until": {
      "enum": [
        "domcontentloaded",
        "load"
      ]
    },
    "default_timeout_ms": {
      "type": "integer",
      "minimum": 1000,
      "maximum": 60000
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "env": "ci",
  "sandbox_flags_set": true,
  "chromium_pinned": true,
  "cache_dir_set": true,
  "close_in_finally": true,
  "default_wait_until": "domcontentloaded",
  "default_timeout_ms": 20000
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "env": "docker",
  "sandbox_flags_set": false,
  "chromium_pinned": false,
  "close_in_finally": false,
  "default_wait_until": "networkidle0"
}
]]></code>
    <note>Docker without --no-sandbox; Chromium not pinned; no finally block; networkidle0 default will hang on SPA.</note>
  </example>

  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <pattern id="f-no-sandbox-in-local">
      <description>--no-sandbox added to local dev launch</description>
      <why>Hides sandbox issues that surface only in container; keep local matching prod policy but with sandbox on so divergence is caught.</why>
    </pattern>
    <pattern id="f-networkidle0-default">
      <description>page.goto without explicit waitUntil; relying on Puppeteer default load</description>
      <why>Violates spa-safe-goto; agent code becomes unpredictable across page types.</why>
    </pattern>
    <pattern id="f-no-finally">
      <description>await browser.close() outside a try/finally</description>
      <why>Violates always-close-browser; throws leak browser processes.</why>
    </pattern>
  </section>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-puppeteer-launch-setup.py">Validator script</reference>
</text>
